{
  "texts": [
    "However, there are challenges associated with understanding the score prediction process, providing feedback based on scores, and the availability of annotated datasets.",
    "In this section, we will delve into these challenges and explore research directions pertaining to AES tasks.",
    "The research in AES faces challenges due to the limited availability of annotated datasets.",
    "The widely used public AES English dataset, ASAP-AES, comprises fewer than 13,000 essays and only includes two prompts with trait-based scores.",
    "This has resulted in a higher number of studies focusing on holistic essay scoring AES models, with less attention given to trait-based AES tasks."
  ]
}